dataPrivacySecurity.dataPrivacySecurity:
Authentication built on top of Ory using OryCloud [1]; Database managed using MongoDB Cloud Atlas; RBAC system to filter admin actions; User is anonymised and data is not accessible in the public APIs; Analytics using umami to ensure data privacy [2];



[1] https://www.ory.sh/
[2] https://umami.is/privacy

